<i>noun</i>: 우려 [우려], 염려 [염ː녀], 아랑곳 [아랑곧], 소관 [소ː관], 걱정 [걱쩡] <i>verb</i>: 관하다 [관하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>우려 [우려]</dt><br>
<dd>worry; concern</dd><br>
<dd>근심하거나 걱정함. 또는 그 근심이나 걱정.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of worrying or being concerned about something; or such a worry or concern.</dd><br>
<dt>염려 [염ː녀]</dt><br>
<dd>concern; worry</dd><br>
<dd>앞으로 생길 일에 대해 불안해하고 걱정함. 또는 그런 걱정.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being anxious and worried about something that has not happened yet; such anxiety.</dd><br>
<dt>아랑곳 [아랑곧]</dt><br>
<dd>concern; interest; attention</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 관심을 갖거나 신경을 쓰는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of paying attention to or taking care of someone or something.</dd><br>
<dt>소관 [소ː관]</dt><br>
<dd>concern; business</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 분야나 일 등에 관계되는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The state relating to a certain field, task, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>걱정 [걱쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. worry; concern; care</dd><br>
<dd>좋지 않은 일이 있을까 봐 두렵고 불안함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of feeling afraid and uneasy, in fear of the possible occurrence of something bad.</dd><br>
<dd>2. scolding; blaming</dd><br>
<dd>아랫사람의 잘못을 꾸짖음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of scolding a younger person for his/her fault.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>관하다 [관하다]</dt><br>
<dd>concern</dd><br>
<dd>말하거나 생각하는 대상으로 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have something as the subject of conversation or thought.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>